abstract: Donald Trump loves to trumpet the hot U.S. stock market as a key achievement of his presidency, and he was in full self-congratulatory mode on that front during Tuesday night's State of the Union address.
snippet: Donald Trump loves to trumpet the hot U.S. stock market as a key achievement of his presidency, and he was in full self-congratulatory mode on that front during Tuesday night's State of the Union address.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - Donald Trump loves to trumpet the hot U.S. stock market as a key achievement of his presidency, and he was in full self-congratulatory mode on that front during Tuesday night's State of the Union address.
headline_main: Trump Touts Stock Market's Record Run, but Who Benefits?
headline_print_headline: Trump Touts Stock Market's Record Run, but Who Benefits?

abstract: The president’s speech was jammed with engineered moments and sweeps stunts — and then came a cable-drama rip.
snippet: The president’s speech was jammed with engineered moments and sweeps stunts — and then came a cable-drama rip.
lead_paragraph: It’s no secret that Donald Trump, just months before he ran for the job of most powerful man in the world, was hosting Season 7 of “The Celebrity Apprentice.” But not all his TV appearances as president have been as reality-fied as one might have expected, especially his sedate, from-the-TelePrompTer State of the Union speeches.

headline_main: Trump’s Reality-TV State of the Union Argues for Another Season

abstract: Hours ahead of his expected acquittal in the Senate impeachment trial, President Trump attacked Speaker Nancy Pelosi on Twitter.
snippet: Hours ahead of his expected acquittal in the Senate impeachment trial, President Trump attacked Speaker Nancy Pelosi on Twitter.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — It was President Trump’s State of the Union address. But it may be remembered for what Speaker Nancy Pelosi did when it was over.

abstract: A day and a half later, we’re still waiting for final results from the Iowa caucuses. But with 71 percent of precincts reporting as of late Tuesday night, Pete Buttigieg held a narrow lead — having earned the most “state delegate equivalents.”
lead_paragraph: A day and a half later, we’re still waiting for final results from the Iowa caucuses. But with 71 percent of precincts reporting as of late Tuesday night, Pete Buttigieg held a narrow lead — having earned the most “state delegate equivalents.”
headline_main: Here’s where we stand on Iowa results.

abstract: The United States is in its 11th year of a record-setting economic expansion, a fact that President Donald Trump is expected to highlight in his State of the Union speech to Congress on Tuesday.

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The United States is in its 11th year of a record-setting economic expansion, a fact that President Donald Trump is expected to highlight in his State of the Union speech to Congress on Tuesday.
headline_main: Great American Comeback? Trump's Economy Has Both Boom and Gloom

abstract: The senator challenged President Trump’s message about a booming economy.
snippet: The senator challenged President Trump’s message about a booming economy.
lead_paragraph: Senator Bernie Sanders responded to President Trump’s State of the Union address with his own speech in Manchester, N.H., on Tuesday night. He challenged Mr. Trump’s claims of a booming economy, saying, “It is only booming for Trump and his billionaire friends.”
